  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactile Soft-Body Physics Gameplay</h2>Your car is made of Jelly. So is the world! <br>Utilize this and your various abilities (Grow, Balloon, Sticky Tires, Rocket, and more) to navigate the levels and find the exit!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/bfa4900312022e94a2bd9226d83d5c4d.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/bfa4900312022e94a2bd9226d83d5c4d.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/bfa4900312022e94a2bd9226d83d5c4d.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Imaginative and Playful Design</h2>Journey through 8 worlds, each with its own theme and gameplay mechanics. <br>Every level has a secret exit to find, as well as multiple optional challenges. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/d2162b7315fa70675e9edd1d34d44b9e.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/d2162b7315fa70675e9edd1d34d44b9e.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/d2162b7315fa70675e9edd1d34d44b9e.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >So much Customization</h2>Draw your own car designs with an in-game paint tool.  <br>You can even record your own sound effects to replace the in-game sounds!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/685af41e0b61f5eb63daa404c092e5e6.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/685af41e0b61f5eb63daa404c092e5e6.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/685af41e0b61f5eb63daa404c092e5e6.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make Your Own Levels</h2>A fully-featured level editor is included to make your own squishy playgrounds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/529d7c35e92d270c541a8555d79e07bd.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/529d7c35e92d270c541a8555d79e07bd.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/529d7c35e92d270c541a8555d79e07bd.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic Levels Return</h2>Classic levels from earlier games in the JellyCar series have been restored and included!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9f51306797b65f94c9b3dcd173beca4e.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9f51306797b65f94c9b3dcd173beca4e.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9f51306797b65f94c9b3dcd173beca4e.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Living Flipbook</h2>The sounds and visuals combine to give the experience of a flipbook animation come to life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9dc47823d0299d596e89c40acf711a3a.poster.avif?t=1724336691\" width=610 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9dc47823d0299d596e89c40acf711a3a.webm?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740930/extras/9dc47823d0299d596e89c40acf711a3a.mp4?t=1724336691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I Remember This Game From My Childhood!</h2>Yay!  After more than 10 years since the last entry in the series, the original creator (Walaber) is back and developing this all-new, modern rendition of the classic JellyCar gameplay.",
